name: Gemini hidden in stained glass
description:
Stained glass has always been a sign of happiness as it brings colorful light to dark places. Here it’s hiding not only a sign, but its associated objects. 

GEMINI TRAITS 

Charismatic 
Uses humor as a crutch 
Could talk to a brick wall 
Arguments as flirting 
Knows a little about everything 

FAMOUS GEMINIS 

Kanye West 
Kendrick Lamar 
Jean-Paul Sartre 
Allen Ginsberg 
Thomas Mann 
Prince 
Laurie Anderson 
Stevie Nicks
